# Church Feedback – stack and patterns

- **DB**: Use Prisma (`lib/db.ts`) for all database access. Schema in `prisma/schema.prisma`.
- **Auth**: Use NextAuth; session from `getServerSession(authOptions)` (from `lib/auth.ts`). Session has `user.id` (PCO person id). Resolve app person with `getOrCreatePersonByPcoId(session.user.id, …)` from `lib/person.ts`.
- **Teams**: From PCO; sync service types → teams → leaders + members in `lib/jobs/sync-pco`. List/sync via `app/api/teams` (optional `serviceTypeId`). Use app `Team.id` when creating feedback.
- **Roles**: Driver = row in `Driver`; Team Leader = row in `Leader` (per team). Check before driver/leader-only actions.
